WEBVTT

00:08:59.703 --> 00:09:01.230
Just in the last few days,

00:09:01.254 --> 00:09:05.863
Sheryl Sandberg has repeated this lie,
that "We are not a media company."

00:09:05.887 --> 00:09:09.332
Facebook has openly embraced
the margins of celebrity

00:09:09.356 --> 00:09:11.730
and the influence of a media company

00:09:11.754 --> 00:09:15.441
yet seems to be allergic
to the responsibilities

00:09:15.465 --> 00:09:16.765
of a media company.

00:09:17.138 --> 00:09:18.746
Imagine McDonald's.

00:09:19.293 --> 00:09:21.722
We find 80 percent of their beef is fake,

00:09:21.746 --> 00:09:23.367
and it's giving us encephalitis,

00:09:23.391 --> 00:09:25.777
and we're making terrible decisions.

00:09:25.801 --> 00:09:28.629
And we say, "McDonald's,
we're pissed off!"

00:09:28.653 --> 00:09:31.584
And they say, "Wait, wait --